{
  "title": "Smoky Oven-Roasted Tunisian Chicken Tagine",
  "description": "A smoky, crispy, and flavorful Tunisian dish featuring the unique spices of shichimi togarashi, slow-cooked to perfection for a date-night dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free"
